&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of experience in copywriting, ideally in an agency or high-growth brand environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong writing fundamentals and a clear point of view—your work is polished, purposeful, and easy to understand.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience creating copy for integrated campaigns and performance channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in writing for digital platforms, especially paid social, video, and web.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Range: you can shift tone, voice, and format depending on the brand, the channel, and the audience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conceptual strength: you can generate ideas, not just lines—and you enjoy pushing beyond the first draft.&lt;/li&gt;
